Value: Sensera Limited, an Internet of Things (IoT) sensor solution provider, designs and manufactures MicroElectroMechanical Systems based sensors and modules in the United States. It offers pressure and electrochemical sensors; microfluidic devices for medical and bioanalytical devices; micromirror arrays for telecommunications/ light detection and ranging, fiber/electro-optic assemblies, and infrared emitters. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Melbourne, Australia.
